name: PassiveExpiringMap_entrySetTest
description: Unit tests for the entrySet method of PassiveExpiringMap, focusing on the behavior with expired and non-expired entries.

test_cases.name: testEntrySetWithExpiredEntries
test_cases.description: Tests the entrySet method when all entries have expired.

test_cases.name: testEntrySetWithNonExpiredEntries
test_cases.description: Tests the entrySet method when all entries are non-expired.

test_cases.name: testEntrySetAfterPartialExpiration
test_cases.description: Tests the entrySet method after some entries have expired and new entries are added.

test_cases.name: testEntrySetAfterClear
test_cases.description: Tests the entrySet method after clearing all entries.
